The old magic of fairy tales and stories is finally showed with the help of the modern digital technology with "iRacconti"!

Fairy tales and children's stories are performed and narrated by professional actors and voice actors.

Leaf through beautiful artworks, specially created to help the reading. Listen the exciting background music.

Do all this in a simple and immediate way, using an user interface specifically designated for this purpose.

For our children, but not just for them...

In this first volume of "iRacconti", the story "The emperor's new suit" by Hans Christian Andersen.

Some features:
* lenght of the fairy tale: approx. 12 minutes;
* professional audio narration;
* watercolor artworks, specially created for this fairy tale;
* exciting background music;
* simple and immediate user interface;
* "interactive" and "read to me" modes.


*** IMPORTANT NOTE: this tale is in Italian only. It will be available in other languages soon.


